author: venrvern
title: venrvern
text: I have a million things on my plate and am on the side of useless when it comes to computers, but George Rusinak was there to hold my hand and walk me through every step of the way. There were times were George had to call me three times for the same file and never showed his frustration. He could not of made things any easier for me. Thank you George for helping me grow my dream.
